OL,3,CGovernment pledges to 'halve sewage
OL,4,Cpollution' by 2030
OL,6,FThe Environment Secretary has pledged
OL,7,Fto cut sewage pollution from water
OL,8,Fcompanies in half by 2030 compared to
OL,9,F2024 levels.
OL,11,FSteve Reed will announce the target as
OL,12,Fhe speaks to the media on Sunday
OL,13,Fmorning.
OL,15,FThe Government said it marks the first
OL,16,Ftime ministers have set a clear target
OL,17,Fon reducing sewage pollution to which
OL,18,Fthey will be held accountable.
