OL,3,CGovernment pledges to 'halve sewage
OL,4,Cpollution' by 2030
OL,6,FIt also aims to cut phosphorus from
OL,7,Ftreated wastewater in half by 2028 ` a
OL,8,Fpollutant that causes algae blooms
OL,9,Fwhich are harmful to wildlife.
OL,11,FThe pledge comes as part of ongoing
OL,12,FGovernment efforts to respond to
OL,13,Fwidespread public anger over record
OL,14,Fsewage spills and rising bills,
OL,15,Fagainst a backdrop of poor governance
OL,16,Fat debt-ridden water firms.
OL,18,FMr Reed said: "Families have watched
OL,19,Ftheir local rivers, coastlines and
OL,20,Flakes suffer from record levels of
OL,21,Fpollution.
