OL,3,CGovernment pledges to 'halve sewage
OL,4,Cpollution' by 2030
OL,6,F"My pledge to you: the Government will
OL,7,Fhalve sewage pollution from water
OL,8,Fcompanies by the end of the decade."
OL,10,FIt comes as ministers brace for the
OL,11,Fpublication of the Independent Water
OL,12,FCommission's landmark review into the
OL,13,Failing water sector on Monday morning.
OL,15,FThe commission was set up by the UK
OL,16,Fand Welsh governments as part of their
OL,17,Fresponse to systemic failures in the
OL,18,Findustry, although ministers have
OL,19,Fruled out nationalising companies.
