OL,6,FThe Government will respond to the
OL,7,Frecommendations in Parliament on
OL,8,FMonday.
OL,10,FOn Friday, the Environment Agency
OL,11,Frevealed that serious pollution
OL,12,Fincidents caused by water firms across
OL,13,FEngland increased by 60% last year
OL,14,Fcompared with 2023.
OL,16,FThe watchdog said companies recorded a
OL,17,Ftotal of 2,801 pollution incidents in
OL,18,F2024, up from 2,174 in 2023.
