OL,6,FOf these, 75 were categorised as
OL,7,Fposing "serious or persistent" harm to
OL,8,Fwildlife and human health ` up from 47
OL,9,Flast year.
OL,11,FMinisters have vowed a "root and
OL,12,Fbranch reform" to the industry and has
OL,13,Fintroduced a package of measures over
OL,14,Fthe last year to cut pollution levels.
OL,16,FThey have banned unfair bonuses for 10
OL,17,Fbosses this year and threatened prison
OL,18,Fsentences for law-breaking executives.
