OL,3,CGovernment pledges to 'halve sewage
OL,4,Cpollution' by 2030
OL,6,F"One of the largest infrastructure
OL,7,Fprojects in England's history will
OL,8,Fclean up our rivers, lakes and seas
OL,9,Ffor good," Mr Reed said.
OL,11,FThe new pledge also includes working
OL,12,Fwith devolved governments to ban wet
OL,13,Fwipes containing plastic across the
OL,14,FUK, continued work on pre-pipe
OL,15,Fmeasures, such as sustainable drainage
OL,16,Fsystems and the start of trials by
OL,17,Fwater companies of nature-based
OL,18,Fsolutions, such as constructed
OL,19,Fwetlands.
