OL,3,CGovernment pledges to 'halve sewage
OL,4,Cpollution' by 2030
OL,6,FIt comes alongside the storm overflow
OL,7,Fdischarge reduction plan, which has
OL,8,Fset targets on reducing spills,
OL,9,Fincluding a 75% reduction in
OL,10,Fdischarging into high priority sites,
OL,11,Fsuch as rare chalk streams, by 2035.
OL,13,FThere is also an already existing
OL,14,Fstatutory target to reduce phosphorus
OL,15,Floadings from treated wastewater by
OL,16,F80% by 2038 against a 2020 baseline as
OL,17,Fwell as an interim goal of a 50%
OL,18,Freduction by the end of January 2028
OL,19,Funder the environmental improvement
OL,20,Fplan (EIP).
