OL,6,FConservative shadow environment
OL,7,Fsecretary Victoria Atkins said:
OL,8,F"Labour came to power with big
OL,9,Fpromises to reform the water system,
OL,10,Fbut so far, they have simply copied
OL,11,Fprevious Conservative government
OL,12,Fpolicy and have done nothing to stop
OL,13,Fwater bill rises.
OL,15,F"Labour must be transparent about
OL,16,Fwhere the #104 billion investment is
OL,17,Fcoming from as some will come through
OL,18,Fcustomer bill rises.
